Account name was being parsed from arn now this is account id. Eustore roughly uses this comparison which is now failing: 
get_user().arn.split(':')[4]=='eucalyptus'


Working Response Example:
{code}
{u'get_user_response': {u'get_user_result': {u'user': {u'arn': u'arn:aws:iam::eucalyptus:user/admin',
    u'path': u'/',
    u'user_id': u'KBCAR8CSZ44Y80FBO3GTD',
    u'user_name': u'admin'}},
  u'response_metadata': {u'request_id': u'7a0084e8-6d02-4a72-945b-fd111460a9c4'}}}
{code}


